title: Opening a restaurant
description:
The Art of Authentic Pizza

A slice of Naples in your hands! Napolita officially opens its doors in Sharm El Sheikh!

Join us for the grand opening. Taste the most delicious pizzas baked in our wood-fired ovens.

title: Grand Egyptian Museum Opening
description: The official opening of the Grand Egyptian Museum, featuring exclusive exhibitions, cultural performances, and a showcase of ancient treasures including the complete Tutankhamun collection.

title: Sohag Folklore Night
description: A night of traditional folk dances, storytelling, and local music celebrating Upper Egyptian heritage.

title: Minya Art Exhibition
description: A modern art exhibition by young Egyptian painters and sculptors

title: Giza Marathon
description: Annual marathon passing by the Great Pyramids, attracting runners from all over the world.

title: Alexandria International Film Night
description: Screening of award-winning international films followed by a Q&A session with directors.
